  </a>

  <label>Irradia√ß√£o solar m√©dia (kWh/m¬≤/dia):</label>
  <input type="number" id="irradiacao" placeholder="Ex: 5.2" step="0.1">
  <a href="https://pvgis.com/en?utm_source=chatgpt.com" target="_blank" class="link-botao">
    üîó Ver irradia√ß√£o solar da sua regi√£o
